</li>

<li>
He never smokes.
</li>

<li>
He never drinks.
</li>

<li>
He seldom drinks carbonated beverages and coffee.
</li>

<li>
He enjoys fried food, grill, barbecue, biscuit, and chocolate. But his body would punish him if he does so.
</li>

<li>
He has been reducing social media usage significantly since 2016. 
</li>

</h4>
</ul>


<h2>
以下可以帮助您快速了解李煜
</h2>

<ul>
<h4>

<li>
